name: personal-portfolio
description: ## To get started 1. Build the `node_modules` folder (if it does not exist) 	```shell 	npm install 	``` 2. Start the Express server 	```shell 	node index.js 	``` 	or, to start and open the page in your browser 	```shell 	npm test 	``` 3. The page will be live at: <http://localhost:3000/>
